//! Project: recall-doctor (cli)
//! AC description: Computes orphans: file IDs present on disk (parsed from frontmatter `id:` field) but not in `memories_meta`. Reports `orphans: [<id>...]` sorted lexicographically.
//! Test predicate: tests/acceptance_ac4.rs
//!
//! Ownership split: this //! header block (AC metadata) is
